queries.query: SELECT count(eventname) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE eventname IN ('flow-established')
SELECT count(allowed) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE str_match(allowed, 'true')
SELECT count(eventname) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE eventname IN ('client-disconnected')
SELECT count(eventname) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE eventname IN ('client-connected')
SELECT count(eventname) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE eventname IN ('ETPRO USER_AGENTS Observed Suspicious UA (Mozilla/5.0)')
SELECT count(allowed) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE str_match(allowed, 'false')
SELECT sourcegatewayregionname as "x_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT sourcegatewayregionname as "x_axis_1", destinationgatewayregionname as "x_axis_2"  FROM "openvpn"  GROUP BY x_axis_1, x_axis_2
SELECT sourceip as "x_axis_1", sourcegatewayregionname as "y_axis_1", count(sourceip) as "z_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  GROUP BY x_axis_1, y_axis_1
SELECT geo_latitude as latitude, geo_longitude as longitude, count(publicip) as weight FROM "openvpn" GROUP BY latitude, longitude
SELECT geo_latitude as latitude, geo_longitude as longitude, count(initiatorname) as weight FROM "openvpn" GROUP BY latitude, longitude
SELECT geo_latitude as latitude, geo_longitude as longitude, count(eventname) as weight FROM "openvpn"  WHERE eventname IN ('client-connected') GROUP BY latitude, longitude

SELECT initiator as "x_axis_1", initiatortype as "x_axis_2", initiatorname as "x_axis_3", initiatorpublicip as "x_axis_4"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE initiatortype IN ('User')  GROUP BY x_axis_1, x_axis_2, x_axis_3, x_axis_4

SELECT initiator as "x_axis_1", initiatortype as "x_axis_2", initiatorname as "x_axis_3", initiatorpublicip as "x_axis_4"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE initiatortype IN ('Device')  GROUP BY x_axis_1, x_axis_2, x_axis_3, x_axis_4

SELECT initiator as "x_axis_1", initiatortype as "x_axis_2", initiatorname as "x_axis_3", initiatorpublicip as "x_axis_4"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE initiatortype IN ('Connector')  GROUP BY x_axis_1, x_axis_2, x_axis_3, x_axis_4
SELECT sourceentitytype as "x_axis_1", count(sourceentitytype) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT destinationentitytype as "x_axis_1", count(destinationentitytype) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  GROUP BY x_axis_1

SELECT initiator as "x_axis_1", allowed as "x_axis_2", histogram(_timestamp) as "x_axis_3"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE initiatortype IN ('User') AND str_match(allowed, 'true')  GROUP BY x_axis_1, x_axis_2, x_axis_3 ORDER BY x_axis_3 DESC

SELECT initiator as "x_axis_1", allowed as "x_axis_2", histogram(_timestamp) as "x_axis_3"  FROM "openvpn"  WHERE initiatortype IN ('User') AND str_match(allowed, 'false')  GROUP BY x_axis_1, x_axis_2, x_axis_3 ORDER BY x_axis_3 DESC
SELECT publicip as "x_axis_1"  FROM "openvpn"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
